{"tid":221780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警隊於警察總部舉行招募日 共收逾2200申請","createTime":"2017-04-29T03:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T04:23:16.000Z","uid":62722,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bc7c94b54f7ae6caf1d588e369b385dc33fb9302","tid":221780,"uid":62722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"警隊舉辦春季招募日，招募見習督察、警員及輔警，共收到超過2200份申請，比去年同期上升21%，總申請人數、投考警員及見習督察的人數，屬歷年同期之冠。<br />\n<br />\n招募日在警察總部舉行，為應徵見習督察的申請人進行初步遴選及安排筆試日期，而投考警員的人士就會有即日初步遴選及小組面試。<br />\n<br />\n2016/17年度，警隊共收到超過20900份職位申請，較上一個財政年度上升17%，投考人數是自2010/11年度以來的新高，而16/17年度招募已達標。"},{"pid":"e7d5feb66813a3a65fbf5974a3d0401ebf4680d3","tid":221780,"uid":9375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"招安。好怕佢收好人搞到收少左壞人破壞治安。"},{"pid":"3fa34710731294f1c50f376fa9afce3e5c63080b","tid":221780,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"連登仔心都碎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d5f8d39b329c853a6a658cdfa546dc79c8ddbb","tid":221780,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:18:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔又輸"},{"pid":"7d5ada21f17b9809d290d4aa72e8b19ac054659f","tid":221780,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:18:40.000Z","msg":"幾時開始可以用錢買個警察位嚟做？好想收片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f4dceb9b46ed80d1c5f834258a92707b547a816","tid":221780,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:19:44.000Z","msg":"而家fg平均都有30k仲考pc"},{"pid":"eda1132865462890e2f548f7879d794acb5be70c","tid":221780,"uid":3794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家fg平均都有30k仲考pc</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ed5fafb5